Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.18,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, who's here this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.59,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.62,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get dumped again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.66,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:33.58,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something, we'll all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.72,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Please help,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.55,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:58.23,Punchline-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch Line
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:26.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Meika, I've gotta ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.66,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing around four this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:31.42,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.46,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Just answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.54,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was around 3:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura showed up all of a sudden \Nand started babbling nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:43.72,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I didn't believe her at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I figured I could at least \Nlook into it for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.19,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.94,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.69,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on,\Nbut the server was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:01.86,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any viruses,\Nand no signs of hacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:07.70,Punchline-Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Fall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:14.46,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Meika used the satellite connection \Nto hack the AFSPC servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:20.03,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The Qmay Group physically \Nintercepted that connection,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using that device.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.99,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,They've already used the \NAFSPC server to launch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:31.04,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,several dozen nuclear missiles \Nfrom the U.S. military satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:36.69,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, they'll arrive at VR-1, \Nwhere they'll all detonate at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:44.49,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That'll change VR-1's trajectory \Njust a little bit—straight for Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:48.74,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:55.46,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity's future has to be\Ndetermined by humanity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.29,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's the law in the spirit world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.60,Punchline-Nine_Years,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}Nine Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.20,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.24,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.70,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.66,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.96,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.23,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.42,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.30,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:56.70,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Guri-chan, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.67,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Guriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.07,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.79,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put some antiseptic on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.60,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.79,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You suck at applying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.22,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I want Guri-chan to spray it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.53,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Guri-chan, spray it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.90,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.98,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:45.33,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! Thanks, Guri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.49,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with the conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.73,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The Human Preservation Project was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.12,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,There's no chance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'll ever arrive at a supremely\Npeaceful and happy future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.60,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how can you be so nonchalant about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.89,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there'll be a next time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.75,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Not for you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:23.40,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I secretly \Nhad a lot of hope for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:30.62,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you could lay down \Na new rail, an unknown future
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like none the world has seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.04,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,But now that it's turned out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:39.46,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm a little disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:44.60,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know you're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.00,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Now you have to prepare for your defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.45,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to tell you \Nwhat you have to do, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.82,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pass the baton to the next Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.94,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Pass on that hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.58,Punchline-Nandala_Gandala,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Indian Holy Text\NNandala Gandala
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.74,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.91,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you {\i1}are{\i0} home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.09,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You look awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.91,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.21,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say you could come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.72,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.52,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.80,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.89,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,"Nandala Gandala"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.04,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Going through your pretentious \Nmiddle school phase?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.23,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,A fantasy diary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.60,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.01,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.78,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you even want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:55.28,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,We're all getting together for hotpot tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.61,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join us, Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:07:59.91,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.46,Punchline-Cell_Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Ito in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:10.23,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ito, have you gotten any weird emails?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.52,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Weird emails?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:15.22,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Telling you to come to the \Nshrine tonight, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:18.31,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:19.87,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.48,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.13,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.91,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.14,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.70,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about that hotpot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.36,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.57,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.19,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's going to stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:46.46,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Ito sure is late, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.25,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.97,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to get milk for Muhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.18,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she went to some farm to milk a cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:58.50,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.66,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:05.94,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:15.61,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.45,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.58,Punchline-Inbox,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Inbox
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.58,Punchline-Mikatan_Text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,To: Narugino Mikatan \N\NSubject: No Title\N\NI have Ito. \NCome to Ishinogari Shrine.\NBring Iridatsu Yuta with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.58,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.75,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.92,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You know I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.93,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoda should be in the hospital, immobilized...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:35.92,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.56,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.74,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.83,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,She's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.58,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the bus hijacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:13.78,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.05,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,That scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.73,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Guriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.09,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange reunion party...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.73,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, it was supposed\Nto be me in Chiyoko's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyoko in Pine's, and Pine in my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.57,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Guri-chan, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.91,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,There's a favor I want to ask of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.25,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.00,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to become Ws.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.93,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,W?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:11:00.08,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so Chiyoko's completely clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.09,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.89,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.14,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Put the gun down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.39,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Put the gun down {\i1}now{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.74,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No, Chiyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.31,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Your body's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:29.25,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.08,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan is my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,precious friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:45.68,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.68,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.32,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.00,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,You're approaching your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.38,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:05.62,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,If you become a W, \Nyour body will recover naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:09.96,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you can stay Uberfied indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.12,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that fabulous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled, Chiyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.34,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Everything he says is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.72,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You can't become a W.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:20.13,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,W's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.76,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lucky it was just a finger you broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:30.10,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,If it had been my arm, it would \Nhave taken three days to fully heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.81,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:36.23,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need Muhi's regenerative\Ncapability to create a W?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.81,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Did Tsubouchi's spirit tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.83,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,That old man didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.46,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Ws are already complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.37,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm living proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.73,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I was giving false reports\Nto Tsubouchi the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.87,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.84,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Because he'd get better otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.88,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,He was finally getting weak from the Uberfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:07.19,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,The Qmay Group's ideals in \Nand of themselves are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:11.98,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I truly love the Qmay Group's teachings, \Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:18.65,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,That old man drowned himself in money \Nand carnal desires from day to day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.46,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm glad he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:25.48,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that perverted,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,vile old man at the top of \Nthe organization forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.66,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Guri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.52,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Guriko doesn't exist in this world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.17,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.30,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Guriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:49.18,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,All suffering in this world stems from\Nthe fact that humanity is imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:54.71,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, humanity must\Nevolve into perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:58.03,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I became his disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.91,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,received a new name,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.88,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,and rose to the top ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:08.45,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, I have full authority \Nover the whole Qmay Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:15.43,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I've waited a long time for\Nthis moment of revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.80,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,All this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:19.96,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.94,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.71,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I've found my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:31.66,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,On December 21st, we miraculously \Nmet again on that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.97,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you, Pine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.98,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this destiny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.16,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Guri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.44,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:45.41,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:49.54,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go shopping \Nand see movies with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.33,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to walk around\Ntown having pancakes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cream anmitsu until \Nwe couldn't eat any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:04.01,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I've been imagining that all this time,\Nwaiting for that day to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.35,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.92,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:12.05,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to being the Guri-chan I loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:20.38,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,The old humanity will soon perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.97,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll cut ties with the \Nimperfect and become a W.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.07,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll let you on our ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:35.08,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,You have two more days until your time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.45,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Think it over just one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.37,Default,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:53.27,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Unbeijini nyopurasara,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:59.18,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put a spell on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:04.61,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Unbeijini nyopurakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:10.30,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to eat up your demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:15.02,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,The magic song isn't working at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.86,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Pine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.51,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's W?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.79,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean, humanity's going to perish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:29.03,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.22,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just ignore it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.22,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a hero of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:44.10,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Saving humanity is the duty I've been given!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.80,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.42,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.67,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:56.87,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I secretly \Nhad a lot of hope for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:00.70,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you could lay down a new rail,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.59,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,an unknown future like none the world has seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.68,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I've been really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.55,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You're insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:09.96,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.20,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I got disowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:13.71,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.71,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect you, Muhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.58,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.88,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.95,Punchline-Flashback,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-tan, hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.95,Punchline-Flashback,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He might hate me if he finds \Nout I'm a fake exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.84,Punchline-Flashback,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:25.44,Punchline-Flashback,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit-san, spirit-san, if you're here, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:24.42,Punchline-Flashback,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.16,Punchline-Flashback,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me, if you're going to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.59,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Iridatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.34,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I was born here in Korai House.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.90,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Strange Juice, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.70,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Who's that, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.35,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the Tou-maker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.59,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Narugino?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:40.23,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.62,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You give me a really nostalgic feeling, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.04,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good evening-ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:42.74,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was thinking we should have a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.10,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.93,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.34,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Korai House is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.67,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you, Pine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:47.73,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Pine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Chiyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.31,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:25.12,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to give up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.78,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there was nothing else we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.02,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.65,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.19,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:40.53,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in this world \Nthat we can't do anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:45.44,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lay down the third rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.43,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a new future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.77,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,A new future?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.94,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a super happy and peaceful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.11,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.58,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.30,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:06.48,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And Meika, and Rabura, and Ito, and Muhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.01,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,All life on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.77,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:19.82,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,And Guri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:25.15,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You'll protect Guri-chan, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:39.18,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuta, this history is a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.44,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a future that mustn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.72,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Change this history.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:50.41,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Many of me have attempted it\Nand made the same mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:55.10,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, I leave my hopes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.74,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, {\i0}all{\i1} of our hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:05.23,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're going to change destiny. History, Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.95,0:22:47.37,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just bust in like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:49.82,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we have an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:51.95,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,An emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:57.27,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkin Chair, I need your \Nhelp to save humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:01.19,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Iridatsu!
